asset.author: Volcom
asset.hookText: The 2nd stop on the 2006/07 North American Peanut Butter and Rail Jam tour went down at Bear Mountain, CA on Saturday, December 16th, 2006. There were over 160 competitors dueling it out for a ton of prizes and a chance to qualify to for a piece of the $30,000 PBRJ Champs in Mammoth on May 19th, 2007. Music by Die Hunns.
